41:03.869 --> 41:05.202
Re-kidnapped herself.

41:05.269 --> 41:06.536
You can't tell people how to feel.

41:06.604 --> 41:08.105
You still upset with me? You still married?

41:08.172 --> 41:09.106
I should have told you.

41:09.173 --> 41:10.573
I was wrong.
- Yeah.

41:10.641 --> 41:12.442
She works at that cute
little boutique downtown.

41:12.510 --> 41:13.743
Hey, ladies, I'm Sarah.

41:13.811 --> 41:16.113
I just testified to keep my dad in jail.

41:16.180 --> 41:17.347
He's not going to get out.

41:17.415 --> 41:18.515
Sarah, what are you doing here?

41:18.582 --> 41:19.716
How old is she, Jared?

